Text: Emergency Maintenance Window pm to pm Cc that runs the process to backup NNGOMAHA will be unavailable from pm to pm Monday November for an emergency scheduled maintenance window During this maintenance window we will be recycling the server to correct an error The only impact is you will be unable to print during this hour window If for any reason this maintenance window is longer than the estimated hours we will update the Help Desk voicemail x with the new estimated time of availability If you have any questions issues or concerns with this scheduled outage please contact the Help Desk at x ETS Omaha Helpdesk x
